{"article_id":"CdiLrPV7uRtWDH1Z","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"If House Republicans thought","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"they were helping President Donald Trump","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"by forcing the release of James Comey 's memos ,","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"they might want to think again .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"The documents","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"written by the then-FBI director ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"detailing his interactions with Trump ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"present a contemporaneous and deeply unflattering view of a President","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"throwing his weight around in his first days in the White House","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"-- that at the very least seems highly inappropriate .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"Only special counsel Robert Mueller can decide","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"whether the stunning accounts of conversations","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"in which the President got the then-FBI director alone in the White House","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"and leaned on him","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"amount to obstruction of justice .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"The Comey memos suggest","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"Trump has a scattershot and self-obsessed mindset ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"brooding about his subordinates , leaks , his campaign and his inaugural crowd size","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"and not appreciating or caring about protocol boundaries","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"that separate the White House and the Justice Department .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"Furthermore , the conversations with Comey","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"soon after Trump moved into the White House","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"paint a picture of a new President","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"more concerned with own fortunes than the burden of his new responsibilities .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"CNN obtained the documents ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"which offer a staggering insider account ,","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"after they were sent to Congress by the Justice Department on Thursday in response to requests from three GOP House committee chairmen on Capitol Hill .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"Trump responded to the release of the memos on Twitter in an apparent attempt","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"to direct conversation away from the embarrassing substance of the documents .","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"`` So General Michael Flynn 's life can be totally destroyed","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"while Shadey James Comey can Leak and Lie","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"and make lots of money from a third rate book","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"( that should never have been written ) .","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"Is that really the way","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"life in America is supposed to work ?","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"I do n't think so ! ''","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Trump tweeted Friday morning .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"Hours earlier , he insisted","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"the memos `` show clearly","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"that there was NO COLLUSION and NO OBSTRUCTION .","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"Also , he leaked classified information .","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"WOW ! Will the Witch Hunt continue ? ''","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"So General Michael Flynn 's life can be totally destroyed","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"while Shadey James Comey can Leak and Lie","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"and make lots of money from a third rate book","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"( that should never have been written ) .","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"Is that really the way","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"life in America is supposed to work ?","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"I do n't think so !","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"April 20 , 2018","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"James Comey","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"Memos just out","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"and show clearly","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"that there was NO COLLUSION and NO OBSTRUCTION .","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"Also , he leaked classified information .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"WOW ! Will the Witch Hunt continue ?","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"April 20 , 2018","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"It 's possible that the House committee chairmen wanted the memos released","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"to undercut Comey 's current book tour","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"and to weaken the Mueller probe .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"`` Honestly , I am aghast","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"that they thought","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"this was going to be helpful to the President","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"and undermine Comey , therefore the FBI , therefore special counsel Mueller , ''","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"Jack Quinn , a former counsel to President Bill Clinton , said Thursday on CNN .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"`` I ca n't get over the fact","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"that they made this calculation .","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"I am sure","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"the President is not going to be sitting up tonight","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"writing thank you letters to them , ''","depth":14},{"id":75,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"If anything , the memos appeared to bolster the credibility of Comey","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"-- given their exhaustive detail .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"Comey will be a key witness in the question","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"of whether Trump obstructed justice","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"by firing him .","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"But it was also unclear whether they showed a clear intention on the part of the President","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"to obstruct justice .","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"Politically , they seem unlikely to shift entrenched perceptions of Trump among his supporters and critics .","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"`` It does n't seem like there is very much new in there , ''","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"Kevin Madden , a Republican strategist , told CNN 's Don Lemon on Thursday night ,","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"also finding nothing likely to change the trajectory of the special counsel investigation .","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"The documents will also renew attention on the odd relationship between Trump and Russian President Vladimir Putin .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"That 's because","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"while noting Trump 's denial about notorious allegations","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"that he watched prostitutes engage in lewd behavior in a Moscow hotel ,","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"they include a bizarre comment by the President about an undated conversation with Putin .","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"`` The President said","depth":15},{"id":93,"text":"the 'hookers thing ' is nonsense","depth":15},{"id":94,"text":"but that Putin had told him","depth":15},{"id":95,"text":"'we have some of the most beautiful hookers in the world '","depth":15},{"id":96,"text":"( He did not say","depth":14},{"id":97,"text":"when Putin had told him this ) , ''","depth":14},{"id":98,"text":"Comey wrote .","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"Trump has vehemently denied the allegation about the prostitutes","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"and it has not been publicly authenticated by US intelligence agencies or news organizations .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"There will also be renewed debate about Trump 's own judgment in personnel matters","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"since Comey writes","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"that he confessed to serious reservations about his first national security adviser , Michael Flynn ,","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"who was fired shortly afterward .","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"Those questions could extend to former White House chief of staff Reince Priebus ,","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"whose inquiry to Comey about Flynn showed an apparent disregard in the White House for the firewall between the FBI and the executive office of the president .","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"Comey writes","depth":14},{"id":108,"text":"that the then-chief of staff asked him","depth":15},{"id":109,"text":"if the FBI had a secret court surveillance order on Flynn .","depth":15},{"id":110,"text":"The FBI director answered the question","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"-- but also rebuked Priebus ,","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"saying","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"it was `` the kind of question","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"that had to be asked","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"and answered through established channels . ''","depth":15},{"id":116,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"Rudy Giuliani joins Trump 's legal team","depth":6},{"id":118,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":6},{"id":119,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"Rudy Giuliani joins Trump 's legal team","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"01:16","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"The documents overshadowed an attempt by Trump","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"to bust out of the deepening morass","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"caused by the Russia investigation and his other legal woes .","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"Trump 's big move Thursday was to recruit a new big-time adviser :","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"former New York Mayor Rudy Giuliani .","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"It 's a wonder","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"it took this long .","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"Like the President , Giuliani is a tough talking New Yorker","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"who relishes a fight","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"and proved his loyalty as a lone voice","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"defending Trump","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"when the `` Access Hollywood '' tape rocked the 2016 campaign .","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"He fits Trump 's template","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"in that he 's a master at mixing it up on cable television","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"and will not hang back","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"if required to lacerate the President 's enemies .","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"Even so , Giuliani struck an almost conciliatory note Thursday ,","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"suggesting","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"that his acquaintance with Mueller could help him `` negotiate '' an end to the Russia investigation .","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"He later told CNN 's Dana Bash","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"that he would ask Mueller for a list of what was needed","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"to `` comply '' with the rest of the investigation","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"as soon as he can","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"-- a process","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"he thought","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"could take a `` couple of weeks . ''","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"Giuliani 's arrival ,","depth":6},{"id":149,"text":"after he was passed over as Trump 's secretary of state and attorney general at the start of the administration ,","depth":6},{"id":150,"text":"raises a number of questions .","depth":5},{"id":151,"text":"First , his history with Trump , matching personality and political experience suggest","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"that he may have as good a chance as anyone","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"at getting his advice","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"to stick with the President .","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"There have been clear signs in recent weeks","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"that Trump has been acting as his own lawyer , with mixed results .","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"`` If Rudy is the guy","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"that the President will listen to ,","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"will keep confidences ,","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"will establish a proper attorney-client relationship ,","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"then that potentially should be useful to him , ''","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"said Carrie Cordero , former counsel to the US assistant attorney general for national security ,","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"told CNN 's Erin Burnett .","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"Giuliani 's legal acumen was proven by a renowned spell as the US attorney for the Southern District of New York","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"before he ran for mayor .","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"But there must be some risk","depth":10},{"id":167,"text":"that his love of the limelight could grate on the President over time , a lesson","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"many Trump aides have had to learn .","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"However , the former New York mayor 's apparent plan","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"to leverage his history with Mueller","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"to speed the end of the investigation","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"seems highly optimistic ,","depth":10},{"id":173,"text":"given the special counsel 's by-the-book style .","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"`` I do n't know","depth":10},{"id":175,"text":"that it changes the dynamic in any way .","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"The idea","depth":11},{"id":177,"text":"that he is going to cause by force of personality , or resume , or anything else Bob Mueller to go away in the course of two weeks","depth":11},{"id":178,"text":"does n't seem very realistic to me , ''","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"Preet Bharara ,","depth":10},{"id":180,"text":"who was fired as the Southern District 's attorney by Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":181,"text":"said on CNN .","depth":9},{"id":182,"text":"Trump ,","depth":7},{"id":183,"text":"who has been searching for white collar representation for weeks ,","depth":7},{"id":184,"text":"also bolstered his legal team with the husband and wife duo of Jane Serene Raskin and Marty Raskin ,","depth":7},{"id":185,"text":"who are criminal defense attorneys from Florida .","depth":7},{"id":186,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":6},{"id":187,"text":"Former Trump lawyer talks about Michael Cohen","depth":6},{"id":188,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":5},{"id":189,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":5},{"id":190,"text":"Former Trump lawyer talks about Michael Cohen","depth":6},{"id":191,"text":"01:27","depth":6},{"id":192,"text":"The President was , meanwhile , consumed by the fallout from the FBI 's raid last week on Michael Cohen , his personal lawyer ,","depth":7},{"id":193,"text":"a source told CNN 's Jeff Zeleny .","depth":7},{"id":194,"text":"Another former Trump attorney , Jay Goldberg , told CNN on Thursday night","depth":8},{"id":195,"text":"that he was concerned","depth":9},{"id":196,"text":"Cohen will lie to prosecutors","depth":10},{"id":197,"text":"to get leniency on his own charges .","depth":10},{"id":198,"text":"Goldberg told CNN 's Gloria Borger on Wednesday","depth":9},{"id":199,"text":"that he had warned Trump in a call last Friday","depth":10},{"id":200,"text":"that Cohen could end up cooperating with prosecutors .","depth":10},{"id":201,"text":"`` Anybody","depth":12},{"id":202,"text":"who is facing 30 years","depth":12},{"id":203,"text":"never stands up , ''","depth":11},{"id":204,"text":"Goldberg says","depth":11},{"id":205,"text":"he told the President .","depth":11},{"id":206,"text":"`` Without exception , a person","depth":11},{"id":207,"text":"facing a prison term","depth":11},{"id":208,"text":"cooperates . ''","depth":10},{"id":209,"text":"Trump 's concern with the plight of Cohen ,","depth":7},{"id":210,"text":"who has been his personal fixer for years","depth":8},{"id":211,"text":"and intimately understands his web of business interests ,","depth":8},{"id":212,"text":"raises the question","depth":7},{"id":213,"text":"of whether the President thinks","depth":8},{"id":214,"text":"that his lawyer committed a crime .","depth":8},{"id":215,"text":"There was a semblance of good news for Trump , though ,","depth":6},{"id":216,"text":"as Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein informed him","depth":7},{"id":217,"text":"he was not a target of the Cohen sweep ,","depth":7},{"id":218,"text":"a source familiar with the matter told CNN 's Jim Acosta .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":437,"left":334,"right":436,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":334,"left":0,"right":333,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":333,"left":245,"right":332,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":245,"left":233,"right":244,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":233,"left":222,"right":232,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":222,"left":221,"right":4,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":221,"left":1,"right":220,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":220,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":232,"left":227,"right":231,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":227,"left":224,"right":226,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":224,"left":223,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":223,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":226,"left":225,"right":10,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":225,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":231,"left":11,"right":230,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":230,"left":229,"right":15,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":229,"left":12,"right":228,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":228,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":244,"left":241,"right":243,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":237,"right":240,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":237,"left":16,"right":236,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":236,"left":17,"right":235,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":235,"left":18,"right":234,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":234,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":